Color   = Black
Rarity  = AI(C1/C2)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = 2B
Artist  = Brian Snoddy / Brian Snoddy

@{b}NOTE@{ub}: There are TWO different artworks for this card.

Text(AI): Target creature gets +2/+0 until end of turn. Draw a card at the
